In[71]:
intertia_scores2=[]
for i in range(1,11):
    kmeans2=KMeans(n_clusters=i)
    kmeans2.fit(df[['Annual Income (k$)','Spending Score (1-100)']])
    intertia_scores2.append(kmeans2.inertia_)
plt.plot(range(1,11),intertia_scores2);
